<bpmn:definitions xmlns:bpmn="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:dc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:di="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" id="Definitions_1" targetNamespace="http://bpmn.io/schema/bpmn"><bpmn:collaboration id="Collaboration_id-ba73de37-caae-4f89-ada3-441f75c3106c"><bpmn:participant id="id-d4bd6e8d-c416-43ed-a4cc-0656146d95ff" name="Cadastro e Validação de Unidade no Sistema" processRef="Process_id-d4bd6e8d-c416-43ed-a4cc-0656146d95ff" /></bpmn:collaboration><bpmn:process id="Process_id-d4bd6e8d-c416-43ed-a4cc-0656146d95ff" name="Cadastro e Validação de Unidade no Sistema"><bpmn:laneSet id="id-d4bd6e8d-c416-43ed-a4cc-0656146d95ff_laneset"><bpmn:lane id="id-62cbe32b-f24c-43d8-9cee-c0a8c8aab7f7" name="Equipe"><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-723730d6-50f0-47ba-af05-29ea2a85be8d</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-02b2b62d-ae3e-4c06-8e85-2b092af3ace4</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-748d05e4-4345-450f-8eff-dfd77eaa8ff2</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-86ee1726-fa17-43b9-8716-ceb2b3372829</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-d39c8423-c271-4fa7-8541-0c60dd5ca5c3</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-4c19694a-5273-40f2-91fb-f6b36e492bf8</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-e1a50127-cb4a-464c-abee-3f4488b6d9f9</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-7458b85c-f7be-42e7-b411-51e2cc3f0c61</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-e9d3f43b-4655-411e-bce4-ba533a5602a7</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-c2029f6e-3321-483e-aadd-221fba4a4190</bpmn:flowNodeRef></bpmn:lane><bpmn:lane id="id-47bd14da-7861-451b-bde0-081eb6834227" name="Gestão"><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-76c10436-929e-444d-b90b-3c027d3caeb6</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-2cfda434-a47a-40ff-89f8-a66edc1d811f</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-913bc3fe-f666-4ce5-891a-eacd9ce3207c</bpmn:flowNodeRef><bpmn:flowNodeRef>id-178bedf7-7ac7-4dec-8a4d-f424e05700f7</bpmn:flowNodeRef></bpmn:lane></bpmn:laneSet><bpmn:startEvent id="id-723730d6-50f0-47ba-af05-29ea2a85be8d" name="Início"><bpmn:outgoing>id-53aabdc7-0a3a-4306-bc56-85f84521be47</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:startEvent><bpmn:userTask id="id-02b2b62d-ae3e-4c06-8e85-2b092af3ace4" name="Cadastrar unidade no sistema"><bpmn:documentation>Equipe cadastra nova unidade (ex: tesouraria) com código e nome. [AMBIGUIDADE: não ficou claro quem executa — assumido como 'Equipe']</bpmn:documentation><bpmn:incoming>id-53aabdc7-0a3a-4306-bc56-85f84521be47</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:incoming>id-a9b5ed83-7858-4c54-bd5c-a067e1c51bcc</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-e842d0a9-78e6-4cc1-882f-d99c3e0bbd7f</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:userTask><bpmn:exclusiveGateway id="id-76c10436-929e-444d-b90b-3c027d3caeb6" name="Validar cadastro da unidade"><bpmn:documentation>Gestor valida o cadastro da unidade. Pode aprovar ou solicitar correção.</bpmn:documentation><bpmn:incoming>id-e842d0a9-78e6-4cc1-882f-d99c3e0bbd7f</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-fde0de21-e624-495f-985f-ca9c188ee92e</bpmn:outgoing><bpmn:outgoing>id-8886a95c-103e-4328-9a44-70ae612a0b79</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:exclusiveGateway><bpmn:userTask id="id-2cfda434-a47a-40ff-89f8-a66edc1d811f" name="Solicitar correção do cadastro"><bpmn:documentation>Gestor devolve o cadastro com indicação dos erros encontrados.</bpmn:documentation><bpmn:incoming>id-fde0de21-e624-495f-985f-ca9c188ee92e</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-54ef376a-a8ae-4df0-be0c-6ebd280742a4</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:userTask><bpmn:userTask id="id-913bc3fe-f666-4ce5-891a-eacd9ce3207c" name="Aprovar cadastro da unidade"><bpmn:documentation>Gestor aprova o cadastro validado.</bpmn:documentation><bpmn:incoming>id-8886a95c-103e-4328-9a44-70ae612a0b79</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-b5bb7bc6-1ed1-4365-8efc-65a547b0507a</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:userTask><bpmn:exclusiveGateway id="id-748d05e4-4345-450f-8eff-dfd77eaa8ff2" name="Escolher rota de trabalho para unidade"><bpmn:documentation>Após aprovação, equipe decide quais atividades realizar para a unidade: catálogo técnico, instrução de trabalho, fluxo, etc. [AMBIGUIDADE: não ficou claro quem executa — assumido como 'Equipe']</bpmn:documentation><bpmn:incoming>id-b5bb7bc6-1ed1-4365-8efc-65a547b0507a</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-0dffa361-625b-4fd5-b774-24ea0ef2841b</bpmn:outgoing><bpmn:outgoing>id-39cbd278-9b1b-4810-9c65-dc7f3769dde3</bpmn:outgoing><bpmn:outgoing>id-1f004e61-a1ae-4c4a-b93b-c476165caadb</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:exclusiveGateway><bpmn:userTask id="id-86ee1726-fa17-43b9-8716-ceb2b3372829" name="Cadastrar catálogo técnico"><bpmn:documentation>Equipe cadastra catálogo técnico para a unidade.</bpmn:documentation><bpmn:incoming>id-0dffa361-625b-4fd5-b774-24ea0ef2841b</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-c567e510-2446-42bc-b6ee-d4a4e51a6612</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:userTask><bpmn:userTask id="id-d39c8423-c271-4fa7-8541-0c60dd5ca5c3" name="Cadastrar instrução de trabalho"><bpmn:documentation>Equipe cadastra instrução de trabalho para a unidade.</bpmn:documentation><bpmn:incoming>id-39cbd278-9b1b-4810-9c65-dc7f3769dde3</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-9ab89eed-a12e-4229-8ee4-410d5c43ab4f</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:userTask><bpmn:userTask id="id-4c19694a-5273-40f2-91fb-f6b36e492bf8" name="Cadastrar fluxo"><bpmn:documentation>Equipe cadastra fluxo para a unidade.</bpmn:documentation><bpmn:incoming>id-1f004e61-a1ae-4c4a-b93b-c476165caadb</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-0ce0f18b-139d-4a27-800e-fceafba842c3</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:userTask><bpmn:userTask id="id-e1a50127-cb4a-464c-abee-3f4488b6d9f9" name="Classificar nível de BI do processo"><bpmn:documentation>Equipe classifica o processo como estratégico, tático ou operacional para definir visibilidade no BI. [AMBIGUIDADE: não ficou claro quem executa — assumido como 'Equipe']</bpmn:documentation><bpmn:incoming>id-123b156b-0b94-4f41-9f71-e865ee80d4c9</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-e2c6bdcc-90c0-4403-aea9-f8b385740389</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:userTask><bpmn:endEvent id="id-7458b85c-f7be-42e7-b411-51e2cc3f0c61" name="Fim"><bpmn:incoming>id-e2c6bdcc-90c0-4403-aea9-f8b385740389</bpmn:incoming></bpmn:endEvent><bpmn:intermediateThrowEvent id="id-178bedf7-7ac7-4dec-8a4d-f424e05700f7" name="L1"><bpmn:incoming>id-54ef376a-a8ae-4df0-be0c-6ebd280742a4</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-0940c1c3-fe46-4b73-ae39-81ae3e46a67a</bpmn:outgoing><bpmn:outgoing>id-eda4b486-66c3-4fe2-8fc4-e6bd148d084c</bpmn:outgoing><bpmn:linkEventDefinition id="id-898e3fd2-fc38-4bfb-92d4-ebe08ad5ce7d" /></bpmn:intermediateThrowEvent><bpmn:intermediateCatchEvent id="id-e9d3f43b-4655-411e-bce4-ba533a5602a7" name="L1"><bpmn:incoming>id-0940c1c3-fe46-4b73-ae39-81ae3e46a67a</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:incoming>id-eda4b486-66c3-4fe2-8fc4-e6bd148d084c</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-a9b5ed83-7858-4c54-bd5c-a067e1c51bcc</bpmn:outgoing><bpmn:linkEventDefinition id="id-2193f9c4-7924-4f71-b5f0-e0e1a1491f22" /></bpmn:intermediateCatchEvent><bpmn:gateway id="id-c2029f6e-3321-483e-aadd-221fba4a4190" name=""><bpmn:incoming>id-c567e510-2446-42bc-b6ee-d4a4e51a6612</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:incoming>id-9ab89eed-a12e-4229-8ee4-410d5c43ab4f</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:incoming>id-0ce0f18b-139d-4a27-800e-fceafba842c3</bpmn:incoming><bpmn:outgoing>id-123b156b-0b94-4f41-9f71-e865ee80d4c9</bpmn:outgoing></bpmn:gateway><bpmn:sequenceFlow id="id-53aabdc7-0a3a-4306-bc56-85f84521be47" name="" sourceRef="id-723730d6-50f0-47ba-af05-29ea2a85be8d" targetRef="id-02b2b62d-ae3e-4c06-8e85-2b092af3ace4" /><bpmn:sequenceFlow id="id-e842d0a9-78e6-4cc1-882f-d99c3e0bbd7f" name="" sourceRef="id-02b2b62d-ae3e-4c06-8e85-2b092af3ace4" targetRef="id-76c10436-929e-444d-b90b-3c027d3caeb6" /><bpmn:sequenceFlow id="id-fde0de21-e624-495f-985f-ca9c188ee92e" name="com erros" sourceRef="id-76c10436-929e-444d-b90b-3c027d3caeb6" targetRef="id-2cfda434-a47a-40ff-89f8-a66edc1d811f" /><bpmn:sequenceFlow id="id-8886a95c-103e-4328-9a44-70ae612a0b79" name="correto" sourceRef="id-76c10436-929e-444d-b90b-3c027d3caeb6" targetRef="id-913bc3fe-f666-4ce5-891a-eacd9ce3207c" /><bpmn:sequenceFlow id="id-54ef376a-a8ae-4